originalText.text: The staff here are so professional, pleasant, and attentive. I visited this location last night with a minor injury, and everyone from the security guard at the door to the staff at the front desk to the physician I saw were so helpful and warm even though I arrived shortly before closing time at almost midnight. The exam room and lobby were clean and welcoming, I was treated quickly, and I felt taken care of throughout the process. I'm grateful for such an easy urgent care experience!

originalText.text: The doctor, medical assistant and front desk person were all so very professional,  pleasant and they really cared about my health and well being. I did not feel rushed and the doctor spoke to me very gently and made sure I understood what he was going to do as far as test, and care, as well as the Medical Assistant.  The front desk person  was so lovely she helped me with my insurance and helped me register eventhough she was very busy and they all did it with smiles on their faces. I really appreciate the service that I received.

originalText.text: An unexpected turn - from heaven to hell. My son had strep throat and saw PA here earlier today. Friendly staff and quick service made us really happy.  Told the pharmacy I would like to use and specified no CVS since we had terrible experience with CVS recently. Arrived requested pharmacy, I was told the Rx was not received. I called UC to resend the Rx and please inform me after it's done. Waited for an hour, no calls back. Checked again, I was told the Rx was resent. However, the pharmacy told me the Rx had been taken by CVS and they were not able to fill it. We were running around chasing my son's Rx for almost 2 hours. We haven't gotten the Rx yet. Why sending Rx to CVS just because CVS is in your system. I told not to do it. Why.... Please ask UC to print out your Rx before you leave the place. Once you left, you are on your own. Don't expect much they will do for you. God bless us.

originalText.text: This has to be the most friendly, well-staffed urgent care I’ve been to. Receptionist Maria was very welcoming, PA Christina was so helpful and informative, Bliss was lovely, and X-ray tech Arnoldo was so patient.
